metadata.title: Sunil Pal's Toxicity Over-EXPOSED
metadata.description:
Today we react to and roast all the outrageous statements made by the comedian Sunil Pal in the last few months on interviews and podcasts

SECOND CHANNEL -
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCwbS7Dyn8RsndtkB6R4AUWw

__________________________________
Instagram/Twitter: @aditminocha
Discord: https://discord.gg/AQH4JYz 
Reddit Memes: https://www.reddit.com/r/aditminocha
__________________________________

SETUP
Camera - https://amzn.to/4eqJx1B
Camera Microphone - https://amzn.to/39nGN41
Tripod - ht
